      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest automotive standards. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine, smoke-free interior. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. A rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising quality and meticulous provenance.",
