      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014not a speck out of place. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
