    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric induction featuring the S54B32 inline-six power plant. This unit showcases perfect mechanical harmony, with a documented VANOS overhaul and rod bearing service to ensure long-term reciprocating reliability. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous transient response, channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission with a high-clamping-force clutch. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement, preserving the structural integrity of the multi-link rear suspension. Every bushing and damper is within factory spec, maintaining the original kinematic excellence and turn-in precision. This is a collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance, optimized for the discerning purist.",
